# ── Go ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Binaries for programs and plugins
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
bin/

# Test binary, built with `go test -c`
*.test

# Code coverage profiles and other test artifacts
*.out
coverage.*
*.coverprofile
profile.cov

# Go workspace file
go.work
go.work.sum

# NOTE: go.sum IS committed (lockfile policy).

